nodes.text: Shajahm-Do was a male Voss Mystic living during the Galactic War between the Galactic Republic and the reconstituted Sith Empire. Shajahm served under the great mystic Dokath-Ra and at one point his master ordered him to found and conducted to him a bounty hunter that was on Voss. Shajahm executed the order but unfortunately the Hunter killed him and Dokath.
